message.body: Are you alive & well? Alex says it's snowing in ny...sunny & warmer (30) here! Still coughing?
Yes! It snowed a little more this morning. I'm still sick and annoyed about it!
Yeah... I'm a little better every day but still coughing & sick of it too. I'll be glad when this week is over. I need it to warm up so I can go outside!
